# DnD Companion — Frontend RTK Query

Sunucu state tek katman: **RTK Query** (`@reduxjs/toolkit/query/react`). Axios, TanStack Query veya ham `fetch` (bootstrap refresh hariç) **yasak**.

Auth memory → `20-frontend-general.mdc`; form mutation kullanımı → `22-frontend-forms.mdc`.

## Store Yapısı

```typescript
// store/index.ts — ✓ Doğru
export const store = configureStore({
  reducer: {
    auth: authReducer,
    [baseApi.reducerPath]: baseApi.reducer,
  },
  middleware: (getDefaultMiddleware) =>
    getDefaultMiddleware().concat(baseApi.middleware),
});

export type RootState = ReturnType<typeof store.getState>;
export type AppDispatch = typeof store.dispatch;
```

Yalnızca `auth` slice + `baseApi` reducer — ekstra global slice ekleme (UI modal state local veya RHF).

## baseApi ve Reauth

```typescript
// store/api/baseApi.ts — ✓ Doğru
const baseQuery = fetchBaseQuery({
  baseUrl: '/api/v1',
  credentials: 'include', // refresh cookie
  prepareHeaders: (headers, { getState }) => {
    const token = (getState() as RootState).auth.accessToken;
    if (token) headers.set('Authorization', `Bearer ${token}`);
    return headers;
  },
});

const baseQueryWithReauth: BaseQueryFn = async (args, api, extraOptions) => {
  let result = await baseQuery(args, api, extraOptions);
  if (result.error?.status === 401) {
    const refresh = await baseQuery(
      { url: '/auth/refresh', method: 'POST' },
      api,
      extraOptions,
    );
    if (refresh.data) {
      const { accessToken, user } = (refresh.data as ApiResponse<RefreshPayload>).data;
      api.dispatch(setCredentials({ accessToken, user }));
      result = await baseQuery(args, api, extraOptions);
    } else {
      api.dispatch(clearCredentials());
    }
  }
  return result;
};

export const baseApi = createApi({
  baseQuery: baseQueryWithReauth,
  tagTypes: [/* aşağıda */],
  endpoints: () => ({}),
});
```

```typescript
// ✗ Yanlış — token localStorage
const token = localStorage.getItem('accessToken');

// ✗ Yanlış — credentials omit (refresh çalışmaz)
fetchBaseQuery({ baseUrl: '/api/v1' });
```

## Tag Types (Pin'li)

`tagTypes` sabit liste — rastgele string tag **yasak**:

`Campaign`, `CampaignList`, `Character`, `CharacterList`, `Homebrew`, `HomebrewList`, `MyCreations`, `Collection`, `DmNote`, `AdminUsers`, `AdminContent`, `User`

Yeni kaynak tipi → tag ekle + bu rule güncelle + `docs/05` Bölüm 4.

## injectEndpoints Pattern

Her domain dosyası `baseApi.injectEndpoints` — ayrı `createApi` **yok**:

```typescript
// store/api/campaignsApi.ts — ✓ Doğru
export const campaignsApi = baseApi.injectEndpoints({
  endpoints: (builder) => ({
    getCampaigns: builder.query<PaginatedResponse<CampaignListItem>, ListQuery>({
      query: (params) => ({ url: '/campaigns', params }),
      providesTags: ['CampaignList'],
    }),
    getCampaign: builder.query<Campaign, string>({
      query: (id) => `/campaigns/${id}`,
      providesTags: (result, error, id) => [{ type: 'Campaign', id }],
    }),
    createCampaign: builder.mutation<Campaign, CreateCampaignInput>({
      query: (body) => ({ url: '/campaigns', method: 'POST', body }),
      invalidatesTags: ['CampaignList'],
    }),
    updateCampaign: builder.mutation<Campaign, { id: string; body: UpdateCampaignInput }>({
      query: ({ id, body }) => ({ url: `/campaigns/${id}`, method: 'PATCH', body }),
      invalidatesTags: (_r, _e, { id }) => ['CampaignList', { type: 'Campaign', id }],
    }),
  }),
});

export const {
  useGetCampaignsQuery,
  useGetCampaignQuery,
  useCreateCampaignMutation,
} = campaignsApi;
```

API modül dosyaları: `authApi`, `campaignsApi`, `charactersApi`, `homebrewApi`, `collectionsApi`, `referenceApi`, `adminApi`, `uploadsApi`.

## Tag Invalidation Matrisi (Özet)

| Mutation | Invalidate |
| --- | --- |
| Campaign CUD | `CampaignList`, `Campaign:{id}` |
| Campaign join/leave | `CampaignList`, `Campaign:{id}` |
| Character CUD | `CharacterList`, `Character:{id}` |
| Character live (REST) | `Character:{id}` veya optimistic |
| Homebrew CUD/publish | `HomebrewList`, `MyCreations`, `Homebrew:{id}` |
| Collection toggle | `Collection` |
| DM Note CRUD | `DmNote:{campaignId}` |
| Admin user actions | `AdminUsers`, `User` |

Tam matris → `docs/05_FRONTEND_SPEC.md` Bölüm 4.

## Response Envelope

API `{ data }` veya liste `{ data, nextCursor, hasMore }`. RTK `transformResponse` gerekirse merkezi helper:

```typescript
// ✓ Doğru — tip güvenli unwrap
transformResponse: (response: ApiResponse<Campaign>) => response.data,

// ✗ Yanlış — envelope'ı UI'a sızdırma
return response; // { data: { data: campaign } } double wrap riski
```

Hata: `FetchBaseQueryError` — `status`, `data.error` (SCREAMING_SNAKE), `data.message` (İngilizce toast).

## Cursor Pagination

Liste query'leri offset **kullanmaz** — `cursor`, `limit` (max 50):

```typescript
// ✓ Doğru
getCampaigns: builder.query({
  query: ({ cursor, limit = 20, search }) => ({
    url: '/campaigns',
    params: { cursor, limit, search },
  }),
}),

// ✗ Yanlış
params: { page: 2, offset: 20 }
```

`usePagination` hook: `fetchMore` + `nextCursor` birleştirme.

## Cache Ayarları

| Ayar | Değer |
| --- | --- |
| `keepUnusedDataFor` | default 60s; `reference/*` 300s |
| `refetchOnReconnect` | true |
| `refetchOnMountOrArgChange` | false (cache yeterli) |

WS push ile güncellenen live fields → refetch yerine cache patch.

## WebSocket Cache Patch

```typescript
// ✓ Doğru — server push → updateQueryData
dispatch(
  charactersApi.util.updateQueryData('getCharacter', characterId, (draft) => {
    if (payload.fields) Object.assign(draft, payload.fields);
    else draft[payload.field] = payload.value;
  }),
);

// Member events → invalidate
dispatch(campaignsApi.util.invalidateTags([{ type: 'Campaign', id: campaignId }]));
```

`useWebSocket` içinde; duplicate listener önlemek için cleanup zorunlu.

## Auth API Slice

| Endpoint | Not |
| --- | --- |
| `login` | `setCredentials` on success |
| `logout` | `clearCredentials` + invalidate all veya resetApiState |
| `register` | no auto-login (email verify) |
| `refresh` | bootstrap + reauth wrapper |

Login mutation `onQueryStarted` veya component'te dispatch `setCredentials`.

### Logout ve Cache Temizliği

```typescript
// ✓ Doğru — logout sonrası
dispatch(clearCredentials());
dispatch(baseApi.util.resetApiState());
disconnectSocket();

// ✗ Yanlış — stale cache ile önceki kullanıcı verisi
dispatch(clearCredentials()); // resetApiState unutuldu
```

## uploadsApi ve referenceApi

`uploadsApi`: `getPresignedUrl` mutation — auth zorunlu; response `uploadUrl`, `publicUrl`. FE doğrudan S3 PUT; RTK sadece presign.

`referenceApi`: public read — `providesTags` uzun TTL (`keepUnusedDataFor: 300`). Auth header opsiyonel.

## Optimistic Updates (Sınırlı)

Collection toggle, live field UI: optimistic `updateQueryData` + rollback `patchResult.undo()` on error. Character builder auto-save **optimistic değil** — debounced PATCH yeterli.

```typescript
// ✓ Doğru — toggle with undo
const patch = dispatch(
  collectionsApi.util.updateQueryData('getCollection', undefined, (draft) => {
    draft.items.push(item);
  }),
);
try {
  await addToCollection(itemId).unwrap();
} catch {
  patch.undo();
}
```

## Prefetch

Liste kart hover: `usePrefetch('getCampaign', { id })` — opsiyonel optimizasyon. Idle prefetch post-MVP.

## Hook Export Konvansiyonu

RTK auto-hooks export et — wrapper hook yalnızca composition için:

```typescript
// ✓ Doğru
export const { useGetCampaignQuery, useUpdateCampaignMutation } = campaignsApi;

// ✗ Yanlış — useCampaignQuery custom fetch
export function useCampaignQuery(id: string) {
  return useEffect(() => { fetch(`/api/v1/campaigns/${id}`)... }, [id]);
}
```

`useAuth` Redux selector — RTK Query değil.

